                115
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                116
                
                    
                // Check if we should retry based on custom predicate

                		
            

            
            

                117
                
                    
                if retryConfig.ShouldRetry != nil && !retryConfig.ShouldRetry(err) {

                		
            

            
            

                118
                
                    
                        return zero, err

                		
            

            
            

                119
                
                    
                }

                		
            

            
            

                120
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                121
                
                    
                sleepDuration := CalculateDelayWithJitter(delay, retryConfig.JitterFactor)

                		
            

            
            

                122
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                123
                
                    
                if retryConfig.LogRetryAttempt {

                		
            

            
            

                124
                
                    
                        logger.Warnf("Attempt %d/%d failed: %v. Retrying in %v...", attempt+1, retryConfig.MaxRetries, err, sleepDuration)

                		
            

            
            

                125
                
                    
                }

                		
            

            
            

                126
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                127
                
                    
                select {

                		
            

            
            

                128
                
                    
                case <-time.After(sleepDuration):

                		
            

            
            

                129
                
                    
                        // Calculate next delay

                		
            

            
            

                130
                
                    
                        delay = CalculateNextDelay(delay, retryConfig.BackoffFactor, retryConfig.MaxDelay)

                		
            

            
            

                131
                
                    
                case <-ctx.Done():

                		
            

            
            

                132
                
                    
                        return zero, ctx.Err()

                		
            

            
            

                133
                
                    
                }

                		
            

            
            

                134
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                135
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                136
                
                    
        return zero, fmt.Errorf("operation failed after %d attempts: %w", retryConfig.MaxRetries, err)

                		
            

            
            

                137

func SecureFloat64() float64 {

func (c *Client) makeGRPCCall(ctx context.Context, conn *grpc.ClientConn, method string, request interface{}, response interface{}) error {

                		
            

            
            

                132
                
                    
        // Create call context with timeout

                		
            

            
            

                133
                
                    
        callCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, c.config.Timeout)

                		
            

            
            

                134
                
                    
        defer cancel()

                		
            

            
            

                135
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                136
                
                    
        // Create gRPC client

                		
            

            
            

                137

                138
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                139
                
                    
        // Convert request to Any

                		
            

            
            

                140

                143
                
                    
                        var err error

                145

                146
                
                    
                                return fmt.Errorf("failed to serialize request: %w", err)

                		
            

            
            

                147
                
                    
                        }

                		
            

            
            

                148

                149

                        jsonData, err := json.Marshal(request)

                		
            

            
            

                151
                
                    
                        if err != nil {

                		
            

            
            

                152
                
                    
                                return fmt.Errorf("failed to serialize request as JSON: %w", err)

                		
            

            
            

                153
                
                    
                        }

                		
            

            
            

                154
                
                    
                        payload = &anypb.Any{

                		
            

            
            

                155

                156
                
                    
                                Value:   jsonData,

                172
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                173

func (p *ConnectionPool) GetConnection(ctx context.Context, address string) (*grpc.ClientConn, error) {

        case conn := <-p.connections:

                55

                64
                
                    
                if len(p.connections) < p.maxSize {

                		
            

            
            

                65
                
                    
                        return p.createConnection(address)

                return conn, nil

        case <-ctx.Done():

                return nil, fmt.Errorf("timeout waiting for connection: %w", ctx.Err())

                		
            

            
            

                75
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                76
                
                    
}

                44

        retryConfig := &retry.RetryConfig{

                		
            

            
            

                50
                
                    
                MaxRetries:      config.MaxRetries,

func (r *RedisRegistry) ListServices(ctx context.Context) ([]rpc.ServiceInfo, error) {

                		
            

            
            

                172

                173
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                174

                175

                177
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                178

                179

                180
                
                    
                // Redis SCAN command directly for better performance with large datasets

                		
            

            
            

                181
                
                    
                keys, err := r.scanKeys(ctx, pattern, cursor, 100)

                		
            

            
            

                182
                
                    
                if err != nil {

                		
            

            
            

                183
                
                    
                        return nil, fmt.Errorf("failed to scan Redis keys: %w", err)

                		
            

            
            

                184

                188

                189
                
                    
                                r.logger.Warnf("Failed to get value for key %s: %v", key, err)

                191

                196

func (r *RedisRegistry) Watch(ctx context.Context, name string) (<-chan rpc.ServiceInfo, error) {

                		
            

            
            

                217
                
                    
        r.watcherMu.Lock()

                		
            

            
            

                218
                
                    
        defer r.watcherMu.Unlock()

                		
            

            
            

                219
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                220
                
                    
        // Create a new channel for this watcher

                		
            

            
            

                221
                
                    
        ch := make(chan rpc.ServiceInfo, r.config.WatchBufferSize)

                		
            

            
            

                222
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                223
                
                    
        if r.watchers[name] == nil {

                		
            

            
            

                224
                
                    
                r.watchers[name] = make([]chan rpc.ServiceInfo, 0)

                		
            

            
            

                225
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                226
                
                    
        r.watchers[name] = append(r.watchers[name], ch)

                		
            

            
            

                227
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                228
                
                    
        // Send initial state if service exists

                		
            

            
            

                229
                
                    
        if info, err := r.GetService(ctx, name); err == nil {

                		
            

            
            

                230
                
                    
                select {

                		
            

            
            

                231
                
                    
                case ch <- *info:

                		
            

            
            

                232
                
                    
                default:

                		
            

            
            

                233
                
                    
                        r.logger.Warnf("Failed to send initial state to watcher for service: %s", name)

                		
            

            
            

                234
                
                    
                }

                		
            

            
            

                235
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                236
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                237
                
                    
        r.logger.Infof("Started watching service: %s", name)

                		
            

            
            

                238
                
                    
        return ch, nil

                		
            

            
            

                239
                
                    
}

func (c *InMemoryCollector) Snapshot() (requests map[string]int64, errors map[string]int64, durationsCount map[string]int64, durationsSumNs map[string]int64) {

                		
            

            
            

                54
                
                    
        c.mu.RLock()

                		
            

            
            

                55
                
                    
        defer c.mu.RUnlock()

                		
            

            
            

                56
                
                    
        req := make(map[string]int64, len(c.requests))

                		
            

            
            

                57
                
                    
        err := make(map[string]int64, len(c.errors))

                		
            

            
            

                58
                
                    
        dcnt := make(map[string]int64, len(c.durationsCount))

                		
            

            
            

                59
                
                    
        dsum := make(map[string]int64, len(c.durationsSumNs))

                		
            

            
            

                60
                
                    
        for k, v := range c.requests {

                		
            

            
            

                61
                
                    
                req[k] = v

                		
            

            
            

                62
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                63
                
                    
        for k, v := range c.errors {

                		
            

            
            

                64
                
                    
                err[k] = v

                		
            

            
            

                65
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                66
                
                    
        for k, v := range c.durationsCount {

                		
            

            
            

                67
                
                    
                dcnt[k] = v

                		
            

            
            

                68
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                69
                
                    
        for k, v := range c.durationsSumNs {

                		
            

            
            

                70
                
                    
                dsum[k] = v

                		
            

            
            

                71
                
                    
        }

                		
            

            
            

                72
                
                    
        return req, err, dcnt, dsum

                		
            

            
            

                73
                
                    
}

func MetricsInterceptor(collector metricspkg.Collector, serviceName string) grpc.UnaryServerInterceptor {

                		
            

            
            

                46
                
                    
        return func(ctx context.Context, req interface{}, info *grpc.UnaryServerInfo, handler grpc.UnaryHandler) (interface{}, error) {

                		
            

            
            

                47

                48
                
                    
                        // No-op if no collector configured

                		
            

            
            

                49

                50

                51
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                52

                55
                
                    
                response, err := handler(ctx, req)

                		
            

            
            

                56
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                57

                58

                59

                60

                61

                62
                
                    

                		
            

            
            

                63
